metadata.description: The voyage begins with the iconic Louis Vuitton trunk. Continually reinvented since its creation 160 years ago, the emblematic piece adopts new forms and materials as a beacon of innovation and creativity for the Maison. Today, Louis Vuitton has created the VIA Treasure Trunk, its first digital collectible, along with upcoming creations designed for those who seek travel that transcends dreams and reality. The trunk embodying the Maisonâ€™s signatures is designed to inspire future creative endeavors.
